In January 2010, Nick Jonas & The Administration began touring in support of their debut album, Who I Am.[53] Apart from guest appearances at specific events, it marks the first time Nick has toured without his brothers, Kevin and Joe. In September 2011 and October 2011, Nick Jonas & The Administration began touring through South America in support of their debut album, Who I Am.[198]
